[src:calculus-of-variations-deep/calculus-of-variations] By Noether's theorem, there is an associated conserved quantity.
[src:calculus-of-variations-deep/calculus-of-variations] In this case, this quantity is the Hamiltonian, the Legendre transform of the Lagrangian, which (often) coincides with the energy of the system.
