[src:calculus-of-variations-deep/geodesic] Here *d*(*S*λ) is the pushforward along the scalar homothety $S_{\lambda }:X\mapsto \lambda X.$ A particular case of a non-linear connection arising in this manner is that associated to a Finsler manifold.
